Journal.Title: Bollettino della Societa italiana di biologia sperimentale

Article.ArticleTitle: [Variability in the dormancy of seeds of Securigera securidaca (L.) Deg. et Dorfl. Preliminary note].

AbstractText: The germination rate of seeds of Securigera securidaca varied abruptly from 0% to 100% in different years of maturation, and this variability did not seem to be due to climatic differences during the period of seed maturation. These seeds showed also polymorphism in colour, which appeared to be related with varying depths of dormancy. This last one seemed to be increased by a short ageing of the seeds.

Article.VernacularTitle: Variabilita' di dormienza nei semi di Securigera securidaca (L.) Deg. et Dorfl. Nota preliminare.
